SIMPLE: inclusive
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inclusive
<hw>In*clu"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>inclusif</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Inclosing; encircling; surrounding.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>inclusive</qex> verge⟦br⟧
Of golden metal that must round my brow.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Comprehending the stated limit or extremes; <as>as,
from Monday to Saturday <ex>inclusive</ex>, that is, taking in both
Monday and Saturday</as>; -- opposed to <contr>exclusive</contr>.</def>
<-- see include, v.t. 2 -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inclusively</ent>⟦br⟧
